text: Gornovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Krasnoyarsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 221 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Ufa, 2 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Gornovo, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
